introduction: Aglam s lǧemla deg Commons d allal i yettaǧǧan aseqdac ad yeglem s lǧemla tiwlafin akked yigburen igetmidyaten deg Wikimidya Commons, war ma ttwabdalent tal tikkelt tewlafin-nni. Tzemṛeḍ ad tissineḍ ugar ɣef waya deg asebter n Wikimidya Commons.
introduction-bugs: Ma tufiḍ-d ibuggen deg ufecku-ya, azen-it-id ma ulac aɣilif ɣer rnu-d tawuri deg Wikimidya Phabricator.
option-display-images: Fren amḍan n tugniwin ara d-yettwaseknen
